## CrewAI Endpoints

### GET /api/v1/crewai/templates

List pre-built crew templates.

**Response** `200 OK`:

```json
[
  { "name": "research", "description": "Research crew for information gathering" },
  { "name": "analysis", "description": "Data analysis crew" }
]
```

### POST /api/v1/crewai/crews/execute

Execute a pre-built crew template.

**Request Body**:

```json
{
  "crew_type": "research",
  "task": "Find the latest trends in AI",
  "verbose": false
}
```

### POST /api/v1/crewai/crews/custom

Build and execute a custom crew from agent/task specs.

**Request Body**:

```json
{
  "agents": [
    { "role": "Researcher", "goal": "Find relevant data", "backstory": "" }
  ],
  "tasks": [
    { "description": "Research the topic", "expected_output": "Summary report", "agent_index": 0 }
  ],
  "process": "sequential"
}
```

### POST /api/v1/crewai/orchestrate

Run HMAS hierarchical multi-agent orchestration.

**Request Body**:

```json
{
  "goal": "Analyze market trends and create a strategy report"
}
```
